  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459450/extras/3a80dd5020d9f80fc4b8c90377022dea.webp?t=1728586438\" width=600 height=46 /></span><br><br><strong>TERO</strong> is a casual horror game that utilizes Japanese folklore and popular stories from the region... experience the terror of the night as you watch a cursed film without permission.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459450/extras/5a22dc5496b4281830c12ae6602821ff.poster.avif?t=1728586438\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459450/extras/5a22dc5496b4281830c12ae6602821ff.webm?t=1728586438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459450/extras/5a22dc5496b4281830c12ae6602821ff.mp4?t=1728586438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Rating:</strong><br><br>Show who the most skilled player is.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459450/extras/2409620583064fd561d0e7267d66b915.webp?t=1728586438\" width=600 height=46 /></span><br><br>Hide if the mother enters the scene, you can watch when she's not around... but don't get caught watching in her presence.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cover yourself with the blanket before she appears.<br><br></li><li>Try to stay alive for as long as possible.<br><br></li><li>Be careful with the bar, if it empties, you are exposed to death...</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459450/extras/Vídeo_sin_título_‐Hecho_con_Clipchamp__1___1___1.gif?t=1728586438\" /></span><br><br><strong>What can you expect?</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Fear:</strong> Experience the surreal terror of being in a room watching a cursed film.<br><br></li><li><strong>Stealth:</strong> Don't let her see you watching the film, hide when she's in the room.<br><br></li><li><strong>Secrets:</strong> The game also contains many hidden secrets.<br><br></li><li><strong>Competition:</strong> Endure the horror, and get your name on the leaderboard.</li></ul><br><strong>By Kanashi Studio</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459450/extras/ac517d53cfc1ffbbd522bc450ec52569.avif?t=1728586438\" width=150 height=150 /></span>",
